programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah seorang ayah mengajar anak tentang konsep memberi, si anak jugak memerhati si ayah yang sentiasa memberi walaupun diri sendiri serba kekurangan. Pesan si ayah "Sedekah & zakat tidak mengurangi harta". Bila dewasa Hashim terlupa tentang pesanan ayah. Hidupnya rasa terhimpit, sehinggalah berjumpa seseorang yang pernah dikenalinya. programme.title: Seleksi Widuri: Keluarga K.A.M.I.L Ep2
programme.desc: Kisah keluarga Rahmat, seorang bekas Ketua Polis Daerah yang bakal bersara, dan isterinya, Kuntum, bersama lima orang anak angkat mereka yang berlainan agama dan bangsa iaitu Karl, Aishah, Mohan, Intan, dan Lynus. Dalam episod ini Rahmat risau penjenayah dikenali sebagai Ray yang telah membunuh ayah Lynus masih belum diberkas. Pada masa sama Rahmat merancang membawa keluarganya berpindah ke kampung setelah bersara. Cadangannya itu disambut baik oleh kesemua anak-anak angkatnya. Sementara itu Ray mengupah orang menculik Lynus namun cubaannya gagal. Karl pula berusaha mencari kerja baru di kampung. Pelakon: Zulkifli Ismail, Khaty Azean, Mas Khan, Neera Azizi, Surya Prasanth Naidu, Eyra Hazali, Adam Aliff Tay.

programme.title: Oh! My Prince Ep3
programme.desc: Keberanian dan kejujuran Danial sedikit sebanyak menyentuh hati Adlina. Danial tidak putus asa untuk memenangi hati Adlina sekalipun Adlina sudah menyatakan dia menyintai Hairi sepenuh hati. Adlina marah apabila Danial menghantar gambar mereka berdua! Cuti semester itu Hadi, abang Adlina mahu Adlina pulang ke kampung. Memandangkan Hairi bercuti bersama keluarganya ke Turki, Adlina tidak punya pilihan selain dari pulang juga.

programme.title: Janji Di Atas ingkar Ep3
programme.desc: Fatimah di temukan pengsan bersimpuh darah di rumahnya. Lintang melarikan diri ketika hendak di nikahkan, kang jaja marah sebaik sahaja tahu Lintang melarikan diri. Farhan yang mencari kerja kerana ingin membiayai ibu Fatimah yang sakit, bertemu dengan Anita dan Poppy. Farhan di tawarkan untuk menikahi Poppy yang telah hamil. Farhan yang diancam oleh Anita untuk menikahi putrinya, di belasah oleh bodyguard anita yang menyebabkan Farhan akhirnya terpaksa menerima tawaran dari anita. Lintang yang melarikan diri bersembunyi di dalam sebuah bas.

programme.title: Matahariku
programme.desc: Manisah kehilangan anaknya yang bernama Mira disebakan kemalangan dan menyalahkan Khairul. Mira yang merupakan penderma organ menderma organnya kepada Alisya. Alisya cuba mencari pewaris kepada penderma organnya dan akhirnya bertemu dengan Manisah. Apabila Manisah dapat tahu hubungan Alisya dengan Khairul membuatkan Manisah bertambah marah. Kesedihan Alisya tiba apabila ibunya meninggal dunia. Manisah yang dapat tahu menenteramkan Alisya bahawa dia sebagai ibu sentiasa ada dengan Alisya.

programme.desc: Aidid kecewa sebab Suzan langsung tak jawab panggilannya. Mujurlah Fara selalu maklumkan hal Suzan padanya. Suzan jadi pendiam dan tertekan sampai jatuh sakit. Mrs Lale mula simpati padanya. Aidid akhirnya bantah kehendak Haryati dan terbang ke Izmir senyap-senyap. Akhirnya, Aidid ambil tindakan berani ketemu dengan Mrs Lale dan akui cintanya pada Suzan. Depan Mrs Lale sendiri Aidid lamar Suzan jadi isterinya dan minta Mrs Lale buat keputusan tentangnya.

Dia mengarahkan PA Faisal untuk mencari Rian di mana sahaja, tidak peduli berapa banyak wang yang perlu dibelanjakan. Sementara itu, Rian di Australia cuba untuk melupakan Adif dan meneruskan hidup bersama bayi Farhan. Dia masih berasa sedih dan rindu. Adif, masih teringatkan Rian walaupun cuba teruskan hidup, akhirnya menerima berita daripada Faisal bahawa mereka telah berjaya menemukan Rian.

programme.desc: Zalia dihina dihadapan keluarga Tengku Zarif.Tengku Zaharah tidak akan menyerahkan walau sesen pun harta kalau Tengku Zarif pilih Zalia.Tengku Zarif bersetuju dan dia berjanji akan cipta SYURGA YANG SEMPURNAuntuk ZALIA.Zalia malu dan lari pulang ke kampung.Tengku Zarif macam orang gila mencari Zalia.Akhirnya Jun teman Zalia bagitahu Zalia ada di kampung.Tengku Zarif cuba memujuk tetapi Zalia tetap berdegil.Tengku Zarif minta restu ayah Zalia iaitu Zahid untuk melamar Zalia tetapi Zahid memberikan syarat.Zahid memberi restu tetapi dia tidak akan menjadi WALI kepada Zalia.Mereka berdua terkejut dan bingung.Zarif bercadang untuk membawa Zalia bernikah di luar negara.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Sekembalinya ke Malaysia, Zafuan maklumkan Juliana dahpun jadi tunang Aidid. Tapi Aidid rahsiakan dari Suzan. Dia bawa Suzan jumpa Haryati untuk terus-terang yang mereka dah bernikah. Tapi Suzan dikejutkan kenyataan pertunangan Aidid dan Juliana. Haryati juga takkan maafkan dia gara-gara babanya. Haryati ugut Aidid nikah juga dengan Juliana, jika tak Aidid akan disingkirkan dari jawatan CEO. Malah Haryati dan Juliana turut jumpa Suzan dan hina dia sebagai perampas dan ambil kesempatan atas kedudukan Aidid. Akhirnya Aidid tak tahan lalu ambil keputusan letak jawatan.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep13
programme.desc: Adif selamatkan Rian yang hampir dilanggar basikal. Di rumah, Rian bersiap untuk pergi, tetapi tidak menemukan kunci dan marah. Adif menghantar bunga putih dan kad ke rumah, tapi Rian terkejut dan segera keluar untuk bertemu Mun dan rakan-rakan yang berusaha lari dari pengintip yang Adif upah untuk bawa Rian ke lapangan terbang. Rian bertemu mama papa dan Afeeq untuk sama sama terbang ke Sydney. Apabila Adif dapat tahu, dia panik mencari Rian di KLIA, tetapi Rian sudah berada di pintu keberangkatan. Mereka terpisah juga walaupun Adif amat sedih tapi tak dapat halang Rian pergi. Rian tinggalkan surat akhir buat Adif tanda dia masih sayang tetapi dia perlu berada jauh daripada Adif demi keselamatan keluarganya dan anak yang akan lahir nanti.

programme.title: Kau Langit Aku Laut
programme.desc: Kisah Anas seorang bekas ketua gangster. Dia telah menjalani hukuman penjara selama 7 tahun atas kesalahan merompak. Setelah dibebaskan, Anas masih dicari oleh saki baki gengnya yang masih mahu Anas kembali menjadi ketua mereka.

programme.title: Syurgaku Tak Sempurna S1 Ep05
programme.desc: Zalia dihina dihadapan keluarga Tengku Zarif.Tengku Zaharah tidak akan menyerahkan walau sesen pun harta kalau Tengku Zarif pilih Zalia.Tengku Zarif bersetuju dan dia berjanji akan cipta SYURGA YANG SEMPURNAuntuk ZALIA.Zalia malu dan lari pulang ke kampung.Tengku Zarif macam orang gila mencari Zalia.Akhirnya Jun teman Zalia bagitahu Zalia ada di kampung.Tengku Zarif cuba memujuk tetapi Zalia tetap berdegil.Tengku Zarif minta restu ayah Zalia iaitu Zahid untuk melamar Zalia tetapi Zahid memberikan syarat.Zahid memberi restu tetapi dia tidak akan menjadi WALI kepada Zalia.Mereka berdua terkejut dan bingung.Zarif bercadang untuk membawa Zalia bernikah di luar negara.

programme.title: Tayangan Perdana Larian Terakhir
programme.desc: Haziq, seorang anak tunggal kepada Mariam yang mempunyai bakat dalam larian pantas, sering berhadapan dengan dugaan kehidupan sehinggakan dia terpaksa meninggalkan ibunya yang sakit. Tanpa disedarinya, pertemuannya dengan Jalal telah memerangkapnya dalam sebuah sindiket jenayah. Walaupun Haziq dijanjikan peluang untuk memperbaiki hidupnya, Amelia sentiasa mengawasi setiap pergerakannya dengan teliti. Larian Terakhir adalah sebuah filem yang menggabungkan genre aksi dan sukan dengan penampilan pelakon-pelakon seperti Fattah Amin, Amyra Rosli, dan Fahrin Ahmad, di mana setiap larian akan sampai ke kemuncaknya.

Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Terowong Ep5
programme.desc: Bertajuk "Rasuah" memaparkan seorang lelaki bernama Imran bermimpi berada di dalam sebuah terowong dan diganggu lembaga setiap malam kerana bimbang akan keselamatan isterinya. Dipaparkan Imran dan Latif rakan setugas yang sedang menguruskan kes sebidang tanah dengan menaikkan nilai tanah kerana berkehendakkan duit rasuah. Isterinya suka berbelanja dengan mewah serta mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakan baiknya. Pada suatu malam beliau bermimpi ternampak hantu pocong dalam keretanya serta menakutkannya. Imran juga ternampak beberapa lembaga yang menyerupainya sedang mengejarnya. Mereka memberi amaran kepada Imran supaya jangan membuat sesuatu perkara yang akan menyusahkan orang lain. Imran juga bermimpi seorang bomoh mahu menolongnya dan Imran menjadi tidak tentu arah bila teringat akan mimpi tersebut. Bomoh itu telah menolong Imran dan isterinya tetapi dengan syarat mereka disuruh mandi bunga. Imran mendapat komisen atas urusan jual tanah itu dan Imran masih diganggu lagi dengan mimpi-mimpi ngeri. Bomoh itu menjelma dihadapan Imran serta mengatakan beliau mesti berani menanggung segala perbuatan rasuahnya. Imran terserempak dengan kawannya berdua-duaan dengan isterinya dan Imran tidak dapat mengawal perasaan marahnya terhadap isterinya dan membunuhnya dengan mencekik serta tidak sengaja. Imran pula mati di dalam terowong itu dan diangkat oleh lembaga hitam tersebut. Kawannya Latif pula mengalami mimpi ngeri yang sama seperti yang dialami oleh Imran.

programme.title: District 13
programme.desc: Terletak di ghetto Paris pada tahun 2010, seorang polis yang menyamar dan bekas samseng cuba menyusup masuk ke dalam kumpulan untuk meredakan bom neutron.

programme.title: Tayangan Perdana Larian Terakhir
programme.desc: Haziq, seorang anak tunggal kepada Mariam yang mempunyai bakat dalam larian pantas, sering berhadapan dengan dugaan kehidupan sehinggakan dia terpaksa meninggalkan ibunya yang sakit. Tanpa disedarinya, pertemuannya dengan Jalal telah memerangkapnya dalam sebuah sindiket jenayah. Walaupun Haziq dijanjikan peluang untuk memperbaiki hidupnya, Amelia sentiasa mengawasi setiap pergerakannya dengan teliti. Larian Terakhir adalah sebuah filem yang menggabungkan genre aksi dan sukan dengan penampilan pelakon-pelakon seperti Fattah Amin, Amyra Rosli, dan Fahrin Ahmad, di mana setiap larian akan sampai ke kemuncaknya.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep6
programme.desc: Haridz dikunjungi seorang lelaki misteri. Ganesh tidak tahu tentang kejadian ini, dia sendiri fikir kes ini sudah habis, namun kemudiannya mayat Pokwe ditemui di kawasan kampung.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep6

programme.title: Plan B Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai dan Mika cuba berlatih menembak beberapa sasaran ke arah botol dari pistol yang dicuri oleh Mika milik ayahnya dan dia merancang untuk merompak syarikat ayahnya. Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Galaxy Games
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang dewasa muda dihantar ke planet yang jauh untuk bersaing dalam permainan Sol Invictus yang berprestij.

programme.title: Hatchet 2
programme.desc: Marybeth melepaskan diri daripada cengkaman pembunuh kediaman paya Victor Crowley. Selepas mengetahui kebenaran tentang hubungan keluarganya dengan orang gila yang memegang kapak, Marybeth kembali ke paya Louisiana bersama-sama dengan tentera pemburu untuk memulihkan mayat keluarganya dan membalas dendam paling berdarah terhadap tukang daging bayou.

programme.title: Kembar Siam
programme.desc: Berwajah serupa namun merupakan dua orang yang berbeza. Dua jejaka dengan kehidupan yang berlainan - seorang ingin menjadi pelakon filem terkenal namun gagal manakala seorang lagi merupakan pelakon filem terkenal namun mengimpikan kebebasan. Mereka bertemu dan merancang sesuatu yang malangnya hanya telah menimbulkan kekacauan dan kekeliruan orang sekeliling.

programme.title: Bumbung Kiah Lantai Tipah
programme.desc: Nor merupakan seorang pemandu teksi yang sudah berkahwin dua . Rumah isteri pertama dan keduanya hanya dipisahkan oleh satu tingkat namun isteri pertamanya Tipah, tidak tahu bahawa Kiah yang tinggal di atas rumahnya adalah madunya begitu juga Kiah. Mereka yang dahulunya sahabat mula bertengkar setelah mengetahui akan hal tersebut.

programme.title: Tak Ori Tapi Ok
programme.desc: Keinginan seorang pengarah filem yang ingin menghasilkan naskhah baru. Yassin mahu melakukan kemunculan semula setelah sekian lama menemui jalan buntu dalam kerjayanya. Menemui seseorang yang mahu membiayai projek terbarunya, dia pun mula mencari pelakon-pelakon untuk membintanginya. Pelbagai rintangan dihadapinya dalam mencari pelakon yang boleh meniru gaya seperti P.Ramlee.

programme.title: Anak Abah
programme.desc: Zarith yang masih menuntut di luar negara terpaksa pulang ke tanah air untuk menjadi pengerusi dan menguruskan resort peninggalan ayahnya yang meninggal secara tiba-tiba akibat serangan jantung.Farhan yang merupakan salah seorang eksekutif resort tersebut tidak bersetuju di atas perlantikan tersebut kerana usia Zarith yang masih terlalu muda dan kurang pengalaman.Mujur ada Pak Din,pembantu peribadi arwah ayahnya dan Nina, setiausaha ayahnya yang selalu mendorong dan menyokong Zarith.

programme.title: Gemerlapan
programme.desc: Mimi mengejutkan ramai pelajar di sebuah kolej berprestij kerana menjadi seorang penggemar muzik dangdut yang tegar. Nel, salah seorang pelajar di situ menganggap muzik dangdut kekampungan dan mereka berdua sering bertengkar kerana hal tersebut. Tetapi tanpa disedari, Nel adalah Mr X yang selama ini merupakan peminat rahsia Mimi dalam diam.

programme.title: Kasih Suami Isteri
programme.desc: Azman dan Akil merupakan rakan sekerja dan juga rakan serumah. Setelah Azman berkahwin dengan Syanie, Akil menjadi segan untuk tinggal serumah kerana tidak mahu menganggu mereka namun Syanie menjodohkan Akil dengan sahabtnya Sally lalu mereka tinggal serumah bersama-sama. Pelbagai kisah menarik dalam kedua-dua pasangan ini dalam melayari bahtera perkahwinan.

programme.title: Tuah
programme.desc: Datuk Shaari dan Shahira diselamatkan oleh seorang lelaki yang mendakwa bahawa dirinya Hang Tuah, seorang pahlawan Melayu di abad ke-15. Meragui kisahnya, mereka membawanya melakukan pemeriksaan fizikal dan mental di hospital, lama-kelamaan Shahira mula mempercayainya. Tuah secara ajaibnya telah dibawa ke zaman moden dan mula mempelajari apa yang terjadi pada masa lalu. Akhirnya, Tuah pulang semula ke tempat asalnya dan mula membetulkan keadaan.

programme.title: Alahai Manisnya Madu
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Zul yang berkahwin dua dan cuba untuk menyembunyikan perihal tersebut dari pengetahun Zian, isteri pertamanya dan Nani, isteri keduanya. Zul berkahwin dengan kedua-dua wanita tersebut hanya selang seminggu sahaja kerana terpikat dengan kedua dua wanita tersebut dalam masa yang sama.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin
programme.desc: Aliah seorang gadis yang ingin berkahwin tetapi mempunyai satu fobia dimana dia takut untuk bersanding dia atas pelamin setelah apa yang terjadi keatas dirinya semasa dia kecil. Dalam masa yang sama, Johari juga mempunyai masalah yang sama dengan Aliah. Mereka telah bertemu di dalam dunia cyber dan beramah mesra dengan perbualan masing-masing sehingga hari ini. Rupa-rupanya ada kenangan di antara mereka berdua. Namun mereka bakal berkahwin dengan pasangan yang berlainan dari mereka dan kedua-duanya perlu bersanding di atas pelamin ketika majlis perkahwinan.

programme.title: Belum Berakhir
programme.desc: Awini seorang penyanyi kelab malam yang pernah menjalin hubungan dengan Fikri kembali menghantui hidup Fikri setelah lelaki itu meninggalkannya setelah berumah tangga dengan Dona. Pelbagai helah dilakukan Awini untuk menjejaskan hubungan Fikri dengan Dona agar Fikri kembali kepadanya.

programme.desc: Daim iaitu bekas tahanan juvana Wira Bakti yang meneruskan persekolahannya di sebuah sekolah telah dibuli dan dimalukan oleh sekumpulan pelajar yang diketuai oleh Adam.Setelah Sekolah Wira Bakti diarahkan penutupannya 6 orang rakan-rakan Daim telah dipindahkan ke Sekolah Indera Sakti.

programme.title: I Miss You II
programme.desc: Persahabatan yang dibangunkan oleh dua kumpulan rakan mesti bekerjasama untuk memelihara maruah juara dunia yodhavathit sekolah itu.

programme.title: Kau Langit Aku Laut
programme.desc: Anas seorang bekas ketua gangster telah menjalani hukuman penjara selama 7 tahun atas kesalahan merompak. Setelah dibebaskan, Anas tak mahu lagi mempertaruhkan hidupnya sebagai penjenayah.

programme.title: Variety Jom Wayang S13 Ep17
programme.desc: Anda kaki wayang? Hos Elyssa Alia membawakan anda informasi menarik bagi filem-filem terpilih tempatan dan luar negara dengan cara yang berbeza yang pastinya akan membuat anda ketawa dan santai sambil menonton Jom Wayang

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep8
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Family Life Lope Bangat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Tara dan Niko merupakan pasangan muda yang berjaya. Namun setelah menikah tiga tahun, mereka belum juga dikaruniai anak.

programme.title: Playboy Dimindaku
programme.desc: Kisah Farid mempunyai banyak personaliti dan kekasih. Dia menggunakan personalitinya untuk berdepan dengan masalah dengan cara membiarkan personalitinya yang lain mengambil alih kekosongan yang dia tinggalkan itu.

programme.title: Surga Mana Yang Kupilih
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Lintang yang terpaksa menunda pernikahannya dengan Hendra kerana tidak tahu siapa sebernanya ibu kandungnya. Adakah ia Niken atau Hasnah?

programme.title: Tayangan Perdana Larian Terakhir
programme.desc: Haziq, seorang anak tunggal kepada Mariam yang mempunyai bakat dalam larian pantas, sering berhadapan dengan dugaan kehidupan sehinggakan dia terpaksa meninggalkan ibunya yang sakit. Tanpa disedarinya, pertemuannya dengan Jalal telah memerangkapnya dalam sebuah sindiket jenayah. Walaupun Haziq dijanjikan peluang untuk memperbaiki hidupnya, Amelia sentiasa mengawasi setiap pergerakannya dengan teliti. Larian Terakhir adalah sebuah filem yang menggabungkan genre aksi dan sukan dengan penampilan pelakon-pelakon seperti Fattah Amin, Amyra Rosli, dan Fahrin Ahmad, di mana setiap larian akan sampai ke kemuncaknya.

programme.title: Nyawa Tak Mau Lepas Kerana Durhaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sulis yang curang dengan suaminya dan derhaka kepada ibunya sendiri. Apakah yang membuatkan Sulis sedar?

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep5
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Cinta Kucing Parsi
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan dua sahabat, Alex dan Ikmal yang hidup menganggur. Dek kerana tidak ada kerja, banyak masa dibuang begitu sahaja.

programme.title: Eva
programme.desc: Seorang wanita yang dari kecil mengimpikan mempunyai kuasa ajaib seperti di miliki sahabatnya . Berhadapan dengan berbagai masalah akibat dirinya yang sering menyendiri dan cuba mencari identiti dirinya sendiri . Akhirnya beliau menyedari bahawa kelebihan yang diharapkannya sesuatu yang bakal memakan dirinya sendiri

programme.title: Doyan Makan Ep15
programme.desc: Doyan Makan menjemput penonton untuk mengikuti perjalanan dan pengalaman kulinari untuk makanan popular di kawasan tersebut, serta akan meninjau informasi tentang tempat, harga dan proses penghasilan makanan yang mereka nikmati.

programme.title: The Sultan S2 Ep5

Rancangan ini turut menampilkan bintang-bintang tetamu Indonesia yang terkenal.

programme.title: Rental Cinta Malah Kena Ulti
programme.desc: Gara-gara sehelai sapu tangan bercorak 'love' merah pemberian Sofia, kehidupan Dendi berubah. Dendi dituduh mahu membalas dendam dengan menggunakan Sofia.

programme.title: Karnaval SCTV 33 Ep21
programme.desc: Setiap tahun, karnival SCTV mempunyai tema yang berbeza. Karnival ini menyajikan acara muzik yang paling menarik dan menampilkan ramai musikus serta selebriti terkemuka tanah air.

programme.title: Cinta Setelah Cinta S2 Ep11
programme.desc: Starla menyangka dia telah menghadapi segalanya, tetapi penipuan Niko jauh lebih mendalam daripada yang disangkanya. Ketika dia terus berusaha mempertahankan perkahwinannya, ancaman baharu muncul. Ayu, yang masih taksub dengan Niko, semakin mengikatnya dalam perangkap dengan menggunakan anak mereka yang belum lahir sebagai umpan. Pada masa yang sama, naluri Starla merasakan ada sesuatu yang tidak kena, dan dia mula diburu oleh bayang-bayang serta rahsia gelap. Dengan keluarganya di ambang bahaya dan emosinya semakin tertekan, adakah Starla mampu melindungi orang-orang tersayang? Atau adakah pengkhianatan Niko akan mendorongnya melangkaui batas yang tidakbolehkembali?

programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep5019
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: May We Chat
programme.desc: Yan, Wei Wei and Yi Ji are three troubled young women from very different backgrounds who met on We Chat, a social media platform, and will do anything to escape each of their troubled lives. When Yan suddenly disappears one day, Wei Wei and Yi Ji start to track her whereabouts, only to find out shocking truths about her that were never revealed.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: May Who?
programme.desc: The story is about a super standard girl in school, May Who, is on a quest to win the love of a school senior heart-throbber, Fame, with her new-found friend, Pong. The only secret is that she can discharge electricity when she gets excited

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boys dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wangs which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Phua Chu Kang: The Movie
programme.desc: Ah Ma visits Phua Chu Kang, who is now based in Malaysia, but soon goes missing. Phua desperately searches for Ah Ma and finds her in a nursing home run by Lim Lau Pek, who unexpectedly offers Phua a renovation job. When suspicious deaths start occurring in the nursing home, Lim becomes the prime suspect. How will Phua resolve this?

programme.title: One Second
programme.desc: Directed by renowned director Zhang Yimou, the film is set during the Cultural Revolution, where a common man escapes a labour camp to find a newsreel that captures his daughter for one second in a movie. On the way, he encounters an orphan who also seeks the movie reel. Can the man finally pass the reel to a projectionist and screen the movie?

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Z Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk is on the case of a corrupt policeman but finds all key witnesses killed when he starts to discover some clues. As investigation continues, Luk uncovers the fraud scheme of an organized corrupt group involving the governments $15 billion Care Fund. He must fight against them to keep Hong Kong corruption free.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Ah Boys to Men
programme.desc: Ken is a rich and spoiled young man reluctant to be enlisted into National Service but must do so by law. He has to endure harsh training but it is made more bearable when he befriends three other recruits. When his girlfriend breaks up with him, Ken tries all ways to escape from camp so as to chase her back, but this leads to dire consequences

programme.title: I Corrupt All Cops
programme.desc: Corruption was rampant in the Hong Kong Police Force in 1960s and 70s. Chief Inspector Lak launders drug money with three other police officers, and a young officer from the newly established Independent Commission Against Corruption division is determined to bring them down.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: There Is No Escape From Fate
programme.desc: Hong Kong businessman Yu and his secretary travel abroad for business meetings. When the secretary is killed in their hotel, Yu is arrested. Despite pleading not guilty, Yu is imprisoned in a cruel multinational prison where the warden enjoys torturing prisoners, and he must find a way to escape from this dark and deadly prison to survive.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughters diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

programme.title: Old Fox
programme.desc: In 1989, young Liao Jie and his father save for a home, unaware of rising property prices. Frustrated by poverty, he learns from their landlord Old Fox who teaches him survival in society. Liao Jie ends up hurting Old Fox with what he has learnt, but his empathy prevents him from becoming like Old Fox.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Call Me Agent
programme.desc: Miu Ling dreams of becoming a secret agent. Even though it seems impossible, she still harbours such a dream and hopes that it will soon come true. One day, Miu Ling rescues an injured secret agent who promises to make her his apprentice. From then on, her life is turned upside down and she goes onto a roller-coaster of madcap adventures.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: Saving General Yang
programme.desc: The Khitan army takes revenge for a past massacre by abducting General Yang Ye and setting up a deadly trap for the seven Yang brothers. Led by the eldest son, the seven brothers set out with a small band of fighters to bring their father home.

programme.title: The Way We Dance
programme.desc: Tofu shop girl Fleur possesses a quirky gift for hip hop and dance which she uses to becomes a supernova in the university dance crew. Meanwhile, Alan, from the Tai Chi Club has an eye for Fleur's sleight of hand and tries to recruit her into his club.

programme.title: Fist of Legend
programme.desc: When Chen Zhen studies in Japan, he finds several Chinese students missing and accidentally uncovers the Black Dragon Societys conspiracy. A new drug is invented to boost bodies of the Japanese troops in war and the Chinese students are used in their experiments. Chen Zhen vows to take down the evil society and destroy their secret laboratory.

programme.title: Clan of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Martial Arts of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: The Spiritual Boxer
programme.desc: One of the first kung fu comedies, this is a story about a con artist who uses kung fu to swindle villagers for money by pretending to be possessed by spirits. When they are threatened by bandits, he must use the same skills for good.

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Call to Arms
programme.desc: The aggressive and dangerous Chin Empire conquers the hard-put Chao kingdom while the Wei empire is drained of its heroes and paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies.

programme.title: Hell Has No Boundary
programme.desc: Cheng Chung (Derek Yee) and May (Liu Hsueh-hua), a pair of lovers working on the police force, camp on an outlying island. Awakened by a strange sound, May goes out onto the beach where a violent frenzy grips her. After her return from leave, May insists Inspector Wang (Yueh Hua) in a bid to rescue some hostages. She shoots the thug under most peculiar circumstances. Then a series of tragedies occur. Her two colleagues die mangled in a lift accident and Inspector Wang is injured at his desk by a snake. Wang's exorcist sister (Hsia Ping), who performs rites for him, also dies in an accident. And so does a fortune-teller who refused to read May's fortune.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: Raw Passions
programme.desc: Mrs Lin's husband and his friend both have affairs with a belly dancer Sasa, and are both blackmailed by her. Sasa is stabbed one day and her brother shows up asking for money. A mysterious man also claims he can offer evidence for cash to help Lins husband. Lin has to unveil the deceit, double-crosses and blackmailing before she is in danger too!

programme.title: The Golden Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman supreme Cheng Pei-pei (Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon) teams up with director/writer/actor Lo Wei (director of Bruce Lee and Jackie Chans first major movies) for an evocative and terrific Martial arts world adventure consisting of a missing blade and a deadly sect of men-hating swordswomen.

programme.title: Little Hero
programme.desc: An orphan, Little Bastard is taken on and trained as a fighter by a hermit. When Little Bastard grows up, he feels he is old enough to go out and look for his parents. Luckily for him, he befriends a beggar, Hsiao Yi, who being street-wise, manages to help him find his family, but somehow gets into trouble with the gang.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: The Invincible Fist
programme.desc: A dedicated chief constable nicknamed The Invincible Fist is chasing after a band of bandits near a village one day and encounters an innocent blind girl. He quickly falls in love with her, but finds out she is the daughter of a vicious bandit. Will he kill the father of his lover?

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: The Pirate
programme.desc: Pirate Chang Pao Chai discovers a leak in his ship after a successful raid on a foreign merchant ship. He goes ashore to get materials to patch up his ship, but encounters corrupt Qing officials oppressing the poor peasants. A good man at heart, he decides to help the peasants and gain a reputation of being a great pirate in the process.

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: When Jianying discovers the Zhao clan's fortune will be left to his brother Yulong, he engineers his parents' death and sends his own son out to kill Yulong.

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: The Lovers Blades, a pair of invincible weapons, are to be delivered to the Qing Emperor. However, they accidentally fell into the hands of Xiao Zhong Hui and Yuan Guan Nan, so Imperial Chief Zhuo Tian Xiong hunts them down for the blades. As the battle begins, the secret of the blades are also revealed.

programme.title: Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Wei Chun is a cocky young man sentenced to jail for killing a man in a fight. One day, Wei Chun picks a fight with a seemingly defenseless old man who completely thrashes him! The old man turns out to be the master of monkey style kung fu and as they become friends, he gives Wei Chun half of a medallion that would direct him to hidden secrets.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: The Magic Blade
programme.desc: The movie depicts Fu Hong Xue fighting against the formidable conspirator Master Yu and seeing through his deception. The brilliantly choreographed fights, glorious settings, superb cinematography and strong casts define this movie as a highpoint in Wu Xia cinema.

programme.title: Apartment for Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: The Sword of Swords
programme.desc: The Sword Master passes on his sword to his disciple Lin before he dies. Another disciple Fang also eyes the sword and plots to take it away from Lin, destroying his family and blinding him in the process. Lin finally battles Fang for revenge and vows to reclaim his sword.

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: Clans of Intrigue
programme.desc: Heroic outlaw Chu Liu Xiang is dining with his friend Monk Wu Hua, when Gong from the Holy Water Palace appears and accuses Chu of stealing the holy water from her Palace and using it for various murders. Chu denies, and is given a month to find the murderer or be killed by Gong. To prove his innocence, Chu decides to investigate the case

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demons clutches.

programme.title: The Long Chase
programme.desc: Governor Yan is killed and his guard Fan identifies Kou as the assassin by his signature weapon, a dart. Kou is listed as a wanted man when he enters the city, but managed to escape arrest with the help of the innkeepers daughter. At the same time, Fan is attacked by a bandit who pretends to be Kou. What are the secret plots behind these attacks?

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma Ep73
programme.desc: The residents of Gokuldham Society encounter several adventures and misadventures as they navigate the ups and downs of life and overcome their struggles together in this animated series.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma Ep74
programme.desc: The residents of Gokuldham Society encounter several adventures and misadventures as they navigate the ups and downs of life and overcome their struggles together in this animated series.

programme.title: Oh My Lallan Ep5
programme.desc: Lallan-a stray dog who lives around a house with 4 other Pets & sneaks into the house for food, water & shelter.The 4 pets' sole mission is to keep this stray dog away from them and the family

programme.desc: Lallan-a stray dog who lives around a house with 4 other Pets & sneaks into the house for food, water & shelter.The 4 pets' sole mission is to keep this stray dog away from them and the family

programme.desc: Lallan-a stray dog who lives around a house with 4 other Pets & sneaks into the house for food, water & shelter.The 4 pets' sole mission is to keep this stray dog away from them and the family

programme.title: Sab Jholmaal Hai Ep26
programme.desc: A hilarious animal chase comedy about the secret life and adventures of a dog, a parrot and twin bobcats living with Ms Katkar.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep31
programme.desc: The Case Of The Pink Lettuces - Something very strange is happening at the farm all Farmer Tom's lettuces have been painted pink! Farmer Tom is really upset so Noddy offers to investigate. After talking to PatPat and Smartysaurus he realises that the Ninjas had asked Smartysaurus to make them pink paint so that they could paint the lettuces. They were using them as pom-poms to cheerlead Pink Ninja as she ran the Toyland Marathon Race! The Ninjas are very sorry that they upset Farmer Tom but he tells them that it's alright. They're welcome to his lettuces but next time, they should ask first! The race takes place and Pink Ninja wins! Thanks Noddy!

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep32
programme.desc: The Case Of The Missing Jigsaw Puzzle Pieces - When some pieces from Big Ears' jigsaw puzzle go missing, Noddy investigates: where are the missing pieces? He soon realises someone must have taken them and draws up a list of suspects. Having discounted the Pirates and then the Naughticorns, Noddy is baffled. But when Pat-Pat and the Pockets invite him to share a piece of toy cake, Noddy suddenly has a breakthrough: maybe it wasn't one toy who took lots of pieces but lots of toys who each took one piece. Cloppycorn, Deltoid, Smartysaurus and Carlton all admit they took one piece. They didn't think they were doing any harm! Big Ears gets all the missing pieces back and everyone is at last able to enjoy his jigsaw puzzle of Toyland. Well done Noddy!

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep31

All the animals had something special; Lion had his mane, Peacock his beautiful tail, Zebra his stripes but Leopard was as plain as plain can be. Then one day Leopard made friends with Puff Adder with his bright colourful spots. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep32
